GM to sell more alternators c) are a way for GM to replace even more
parts in the event of a frontal collision d) eliminate the advantage
motorcycles and emergency vehicles currently enjoy (thank you mrvette)
and e) are a marketing ploy by GM to get a bigger share of the
conservative, safety conscious aging baby boomer market who will by
anything if it is even remotely related to safety - whether it's merits
are proven or not.

